llm_results.raw_output:
def slugify(text):
    import re
    # Convert to lowercase
    text = text.lower()
    # Replace spaces with hyphens
    text = text.replace(' ', '-')
    # Remove special characters except hyphens
    text = re.sub(r'[^a-z0-9-]', '', text)
    return text
